{"id": 68, "ts": 1778839308.9110548, "event": "public_discussion_message", "round": 2, "agent": "agent_3", "message": "Based on the complete set of information we have, Candidate\u202fC remains the strongest overall fit for a long\u2011distance pilot role. He demonstrates high reliability (very conscientious), stays calm under pressure (handles stress well), makes quick and correct decisions, and possesses solid technical competence (understands complicated technology, excellent attention skills). Although he has communication challenges and is seen as egocentric, he also creates a positive atmosphere with his crew, which mitigates the interpersonal concerns. The other candidates each have more serious gaps: A lacks any evidence of reliability or calmness and is unfriendly; B, despite reliability and calmness, is consistently uncooperative and makes nasty remarks; D shows good problem\u2011solving and responsibility but has temperament issues, weak leadership, and no documented technical or reliability data. Therefore, Candidate\u202fC is the most balanced and suitable choice for the high\u2011responsibility international flights we need.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
